## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ”— Classify image URLs
- ğŸ“ Upload and classify video files
- ğŸ§  Batch image classification
- ğŸ©º Health check endpoint
- ğŸ³ Fully containerized

---

## ğŸ“¦ Requirements

- Docker installed
- Internet connection (for downloading model weights the first time)

